{"tid":2500276,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教局再推8科國安教育框架 企會財學中港經濟「唇齒相依」 健社科學信權威免影響抗疫","createTime":"2021-04-22T13:23:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T16:26:38.000Z","uid":223531,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"98620ef4fc93a6fabf4de6d628421ca092ec3f79","tid":2500276,"uid":223531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:23:47.000Z","msg":"教育局再推出8科的國家安全教育課程文件，包括中文、科技教育、企會財（BAFS）、健康管理與社會關懷、資訊及通訊科技（ICT）、科學、化學和物理科。其中BAFS科要討論中美貿易戰和一帶一路，了解香港作為中國一部份，與內地經濟「唇齒相依」；健康管理與社會關懷科要學習傳染病問題要參考「具權威的來源」，不應輕率轉發以免「影響抗疫工作」；科學科亦要認識香港食水來源和討論缺水的負面影響、知道「國家對人民健康的重視」，以及到大灣區考察等&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;中文科方面，小學生要學習名人傳記，培養家國情懷，並在普通話科學習慣用語、謙敬語、委婉語和禁忌語等&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210422/UZ7B3Z3ENVFCBFYHZDL26TYQ2U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210422%2FUZ7B3Z3ENVFCBFYHZDL26TYQ2U%2F&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrSWHaP8IcnP89ZPrefCyuoo%3D&h=52d531e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210422%2FUZ7B3Z3ENVFCBFYHZDL26TYQ2U%2F&h=be1ce603\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210422/UZ7B3Z3ENVFCBFYHZDL26TYQ2U/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"affa09be8095cfa22d4a02e19da9a2333e435f1f","tid":2500276,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b6ab11f79ac31c4dd7c8527073f320e5e9dbff","tid":2500276,"uid":363016,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:35:00.000Z","msg":"數學都可以加個國安教育 加埋習近平語錄係考題上都得"},{"pid":"5580ff36f9cad77c40ec3093f46d5cd513d3b91b","tid":2500276,"